Kitchenette very limited facilities but great for cooking English Breakfast every day and then loading dishwasher as we went out.	Laundry facilities were available, but, with four very cheap laundries with in a block or so, it is hardly worth availing oneself of this facility.	Desk staff and door man very helpful - we needed extra wine glasses and an extra frying pan and they were cheerfully provided.	And on top off their lumpy beds and old pillows are Pink Sheets, is a Black floral print duvet covers that come complete with a weathered “Butt Print” at the edge of the bed to showcase where people have been sitting down over the last 40 years!